<p>I’m reading about Slots and Fills and it doesn’t appear that either theme is taking advantage of the Slots and Fills core concept here: <a href="https://docs.frontity.org/learning-frontity/roots" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">https://docs.frontity.org/learning-frontity/roots</a></p>
<p>I did a search for slot,Slot,fill,Fill and none of the variations are turning up search results in mars-theme or frontity-chakra-theme.</p>
<p>Maybe both themes were developed before these features were released?<br>
</p><aside class="quote quote-modified" data-post="1" data-topic="895">
  <div class="title">
